### Global Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@fileId = 9a4e4e1e-629d-4bf9-aa19-6111b8110c92

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### List Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### Upload File
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello RustFS! This is a test file.
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Test file upload via REST Client
--WebAppBoundary--

### Get File Metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}
Accept: application/json

### Download File
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}/download

### Get Presigned URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}/presigned-url?expiry=3600
Accept: application/json

### Delete File
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}
Accept: application/json
